]</span></span></h2>\n<div><div class=\"seealso\">The following text is transcluded from <a href=\"/w/Transcript:Giant_champion_scroll\" title=\"Transcript:Giant champion scroll\">Transcript:Giant champion scroll</a>.</div><div class=\"transcript\">\n<p>Get yourself to the Champions' Guild, if you dare to face me puny human.\n</p>\nChampion of Giants</div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Giant_champion_scroll?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Giant_champion_scroll?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td data-sort-value=\"16 December 2021\"><a href=\"/w/16_December\" title=\"16 December\">16&#160;December</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Christmas_2021\" title=\"Update:Christmas 2021\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>If a Champion's scroll would have dropped as a duplicate, the game message \"<i><span style=\"color:#990000;\">You have a funny feeling that you would have received a Champion's scroll...</span></i>\" appears now.\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td data-sort-value=\"14 September 2017\"><a href=\"/w/14_September\" title=\"14 September\">14&#160;September</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2017\" title=\"2017\">2017</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Fossil_Island_changes\" title=\"Update:Fossil Island changes\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>The item was renamed from \"Champion scroll\" to \"Giant champion scroll\".\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td data-sort-value=\"25 June 2015\"><a href=\"/w/25_June\" title=\"25 June\">25&#160;June</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2015\" title=\"2015\">2015</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Boss_Room_Counters_%26_Platinum_Tokens\" title=\"Update:Boss Room Counters &amp; Platinum Tokens\">update</a>&#160;|&#160;<a href=\"/w/Poll:Old_School_Content_Poll_34:_XP_droplets_%26_Slayer\" title=\"Poll:Old School Content Poll 34: XP droplets &amp; Slayer\">poll</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Players will now receive a coloured message in their chat box upon receiving a champion scroll drop.\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Champions\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Champions\" title=\"Template:Champions\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Champions\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Champions?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Champions%27_Challenge\" title=\"Champions&#39; Challenge\">Champions' Challenge</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Lower Champions</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Earth_Warrior_Champion\" title=\"Earth Warrior Champion\">Earth Warrior</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Ghoul_Champion\" title=\"Ghoul Champion\">Ghoul</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Giant_Champion\" title=\"Giant Champion\">Giant</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Goblin_Cham