ion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  153.775      1 -total\n 29.90%   45.982      1 Template:Drop_sources\n 27.58%   42.413      1 Template:Infobox_Item\n 14.52%   22.321      1 Template:Champions\n 10.42%   16.024      1 Template:Hastranscript\n  9.99%   15.365      1 Template:Navbox\n  8.68%   13.350      1 Template:External\n  4.77%    7.333      3 Template:Subject_changes\n  2.79%    4.286      1 Template:Ctg\n  2.09%    3.216     13 Template:Plink\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:18987-0!canonical and timestamp 20220517030739 and revision id 14264235. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs}}\n{{Infobox Item\n|name = Giant champion scroll\n|image = [[File:Giant champion scroll.png]]\n|release = [[12 December]] [[2005]]\n|update = Champions, Wyverns and Granite\n|members = Yes\n|quest = No\n|tradeable = No\n|placeholder = Yes\n|equipable = No\n|stackable = No\n|noteable = No\n|options = Read\n|destroy = Drop\n|examine = It's a challenge from the Giant Champion!\n|value = 1\n|weight = 0.001\n|id = 6800\n}}\n[[File:Giant champion scroll detail.png|left|150px]]\nThe '''giant champion scroll''' is an extremely rare drop from various giants. It contains a challenge from the [[Giant Champion]]. In order to be eligible to receive the scroll, players must be on a [[members]] server and have 32 [[quest point]]s.\n\nBy bringing this scroll to [[Larxus]] in the basement of [[Champions' Guild]], players may fight the [[Giant Champion]] as part of the [[Champions' Challenge]] [[minigame]]. During the fight, players can only use [[melee]] attacks.\n\nNote that the Hill Giant spawn near [[Shayzien]] is a great place to setup a cannon to farm kills.\n\n{{Clear|left}}\n\n==Item sources==\n{{Drop sources|Giant champion scroll}}\n\n==Transcript==\n{{Hastranscript|Giant champion scroll|transclude=yes}}\n\n==Changes==\n{{Subject changes header}}\n{{Subject changes\n|date = 16 December 2021\n|update = Christmas 2021\n|poll = \n|change = If a Champion's scroll would have dropped as a duplicate, the game message \"''{{Colour|#990000|You have a funny feeling that you would have received a Champion's scroll...}}''\" appears now.\n}}\n{{Subject changes\n|date = 14 September 2017\n|update = Fossil Island changes\n|change = The item was renamed from \"Champion scroll\" to \"Giant champion scroll\".\n}}\n{{Subject changes\n|date = 25 June 2015\n|update = Boss Room Counters & Platinum Tokens\n|poll = Old School Content Poll 34: XP droplets & Slayer\n|change = Players will now receive a coloured message in their chat box upon receiving a champion scroll drop.\n}}\n{{Subject changes footer}}\n\n{{Champions}}\n[[Category:Texts and tomes]]"}